<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Aaron Headley Audio</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="Corporate A1, A2, RF Coordination, Intercom, Systems, and Production Management by Aaron Headley." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050509;
      --bg-alt: #0c0c15;
      --accent: #ffcc33;
      --accent-soft: rgba(255, 204, 51, 0.15);
      --text: #f5f5f7;
      --muted: #a0a0b2;
      --border-subtle: #262637;
      --card-bg: #11111c;
      --pill-bg: #181824;
      --danger: #ff4b4b;
      --max-width: 1100px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #181824 0, #050509 55%);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5,5,9,0.95), rgba(5,5,9,0.6));
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .logo-initials {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffcc33, #ff7a18);
      color: #050509;
    }

    .logo-text {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .logo-text span:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .logo-text span:last-child {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    }

    nav a {
      color: var(--muted);
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    nav a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 0%;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--accent);
      transition: width 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    nav a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,204,51,0.5);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-cta span {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      padding-top: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-kicker::before {
      content: "";
      width: 32px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--accent));
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.1rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero-title span {
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-title span.highlight {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      max-width: 34rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .hero-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .pill {
      padding: 0.28rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--pill-bg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .pill-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-ghost {
      padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcc33, #ff7a18);
      color: #050509;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255,204,51,0.25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.05);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero-footnote {
      margin-top: 1.7rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-footnote strong {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero-footnote span.divider {
      width: 18px;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }

    .hero-right {
      position: relative;
    }

    .card {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1e1e2b, #090912);
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 1.25rem 1.3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-image-placeholder {
      border-radius: 0.9rem;
      min-height: 260px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        #181824,
        #181824 10px,
        #141420 10px,
        #141420 20px
      );
      border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .meta-item {
      padding: 0.7rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      background: rgba(8,8,16,0.85);
    }

    .meta-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .meta-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .about-text p {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .about-callout {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.9rem;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      background: rgba(12,12,24,0.9);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .about-meta-card {
      padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #101020, #050509);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .about-meta-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .about-meta-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
    }

    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .tag-chip {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .services {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #181824 0, #050509 60%);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 1.2rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: rgba(9,9,18,0.96);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .service-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .service-body {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .service-footer {
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .service-footer span {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .work-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }

    .work-card {
      padding: 1.1rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: rgba(9,9,18,0.9);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      font-size: 0.87rem;
    }

    .work-role {
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .work-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .work-description {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .work-tags {
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .contact {
      padding-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .contact-card {
      padding: 1.4rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 1.1rem;
      background: rgba(9,9,18,0.96);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .contact-card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .contact-card p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .field {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .field label {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .field input,
    .field textarea {
      background: rgba(5,5,12,0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius: 0.6rem;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .field textarea {
      min-height: 110px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,204,51,0.45);
    }

    .contact-sidebar {
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-chip {
      margin-top: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      background: rgba(8,8,16,0.9);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .contact-sidebar a {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.25rem 1.6rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }
      .hero-right {
        order: -1;
      }
      .about-grid,
      .services-grid,
      .work-grid,
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
      .services-grid {
        gap: 1.1rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .nav-inner {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.8rem;
      }
      nav {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }
      .section {
        padding-inline: 1rem;
      }
      .hero {
        padding-top: 2.3rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="#top" class="logo-mark">
          <div class="logo-initials">AH</div>
          <div class="logo-text">
            <span>Live / Corporate</span>
            <span>Aaron Headley Audio</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <nav>
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#services">Services</a>
          <a href="#work">Work</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">
            <span>●</span>
            Book a show
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="top">
      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="section hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-kicker">Corporate A1 • RF • Systems</div>
          <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-title">
            <span>I help shows</span>
            <span class="highlight">cut through the noise.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            I design, mix, and support live and virtual events so the message lands 
            clearly the first time—no drama, no surprises, and no missed cues.[web:5]
          </p>

          <div class="hero-tags">
            <div class="pill">
              <span class="pill-dot"></span>
              Corporate A1 / A2
            </div>
            <div class="pill">
              <span class="pill-dot"></span>
              RF coordination &amp; intercom
            </div>
            <div class="pill">
              <span class="pill-dot"></span>
              System design &amp; deployment
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">
              Schedule a show brief →
            </a>
            <a href="#work" class="btn-ghost">
              Browse recent work
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-footnote">
            <span><strong>25+ years</strong> in corporate, broadcast, and live events.[web:5]</span>
            <span class="divider"></span>
            <span>Digital consoles, RF, comms, and systems that just work.[web:5]</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-right">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="hero-image-placeholder">
              Image to come
            </div>
            <div class="hero-meta">
              <div class="meta-item">
                <div class="meta-label">Primary roles</div>
                <div class="meta-value">
                  Corporate A1, A2, RFPL, Intercom, Systems[web:5]
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <div class="meta-label">Based in</div>
                <div class="meta-value">
                  NYC Metro • Available to travel[web:5]
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <div class="meta-label">Specialties</div>
                <div class="meta-value">
                  Digital consoles, RF planning, comms, system design[web:5]
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <div class="meta-label">Tools</div>
                <div class="meta-value">
                  Dante, Smaart, Signal Hound, Vectorworks, Riedel[web:5]
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ABOUT -->
      <section class="section" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title" id="about-title">About</h2>
          <div class="section-kicker">Facilitating communication</div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              My mission is simple: facilitate communication. In an information‑saturated 
              environment, it takes intentional systems and calm execution to make sure 
              the right people hear the right message at the right time.[web:5]
            </p>
            <p>
              I have spent more than 25 years partnering with marketers, producers, 
              and technical teams, guiding messaging and deploying the right audio and 
              comms solutions so executives and presenters can focus on content—not gear.[web:5]
            </p>
            <p>
              I am as comfortable troubleshooting RF in a crowded ballroom as I am 
              driving a digital console or aligning a PA. The goal is always the same: 
              clean, intelligible audio and a crew that trusts the plan.[web:5]
            </p>
            <div class="about-callout">
              I work as a freelance audio specialist—Corporate A1, A2, RFPL, system 
              designer, and production manager—plugging into existing teams and helping 
              them deliver reliable shows in high‑pressure environments.[web:5]
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="about-meta-card">
            <div>
              <div class="about-meta-label">Core roles</div>
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag-chip">Corporate A1 / A2[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">RF coordination &amp; RFPL[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Intercom programming[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">System design[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Production management[web:5]</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-meta-row">
              <div>
                <div class="about-meta-label">Experience</div>
                <div>25+ years in audio &amp; events[web:5]</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="about-meta-label">Location</div>
                <div>New York City Metro[web:5]</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div class="about-meta-label">Selected tools</div>
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag-chip">Digital mixing consoles[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Signal Hound analyzers[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Riedel / Clear-Com / RTS[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">L‑Acoustics Soundvision[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Smaart acoustic analysis[web:5]</span>
                <span class="tag-chip">Vectorworks CAD[web:5]</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- SERVICES -->
      <section class="section services" id="services" aria-labelledby="services-title">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title" id="services-title">Services</h2>
          <div class="section-kicker">How I plug into teams</div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-grid">
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-title">Corporate A1 / A2</div>
            <div class="service-body">
              Primary and secondary audio support for corporate, broadcast, and hybrid 
              events—console operation, playback, routing, and backstage coordination 
              so the program feels effortless from the audience.[web:5]
            </div>
            <div class="service-footer">
              Typical scope: <span>general sessions, keynotes, town halls</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-title">RF &amp; Intercom</div>
            <div class="service-body">
              RF planning and coordination using Signal Hound and industry tools, along 
              with programming and deployment of Riedel, Clear-Com, and RTS systems 
              to keep crews connected without dropouts.[web:5]
